# {{ .name }}

An Intropy **extractor block**: reads from the `{{ .sourceSystem }}` external
system and publishes onto the `{{ .publishesTopic }}` topic. How the source is
reached (the transport) is chosen later, at `intropy system create`.

This component's edge intent is recorded in `.intropy/scaffold.json`. Scaffold
the other components of your system next to this folder, then generate a wired
SystemHost from the parent directory:

```bash
intropy system create -n <system-name>
dotnet run --project <SystemName>.SystemHost -- check   # validate the topology
dotnet run --project <SystemName>.SystemHost            # run the system locally
```
